* Carnage snarled when she was suddenly attacked from her side, instead of 
leaping back to safety she plowed head on and jaws open into her attacker.
She felt the satisfying rip of torn flesh as her jaws tore into her 
attackers hide and locked her jaw in place when she felt the pulsing jugular 
brush against her tongue.
She had been attacked dozens of times back on Cybertron, many had attacked 
in worse ways then this!
Carnage looked at her attacker as she sank her jaws even deeper into it's 
neck, it was another raptor! She judged it's weight and height as she kicked 
her legs up and fastened them into the structure of the carnivour, it was an 
inch taller then she was but only a few ounces heavier.
She dug her front claws into the back of the raptor's head and clung on with 
both front and back.
Carnage ripped and tore into the hide of her attacker, feeling a jolt 
through her claws as she racked over an occasional structure beam.
NO ONE TOOK HER BY SURPRISE AND GOT AWAY WITH IT!!!!!*
